window.bookSummaryJSON = "When Tommy and Tuppence visit an elderly aunt in her gothic nursing home, they think nothing of her mistrust of the doctors; after all, Ada is a very difficult old lady. <p>But when Mrs Lockett mentions a poisoned mushroom stew, and Mrs Lancaster talks about \"something behind the fireplace\", Tommy and Tuppence find themselves caught up in an unexpected adventure involving possible black magic.</p>"; 
